The light bulb's broken?

39
00:02:21,020 --> 00:02:23,870
♪I want you to be with me forever♪

40
00:02:24,260 --> 00:02:25,140
Let me smell it.

41
00:02:25,280 --> 00:02:29,710
♪Shining with me♪

42
00:02:30,660 --> 00:02:31,860
Why drink this?

43
00:02:31,860 --> 00:02:33,100
It can make you dumb.

44
00:02:33,620 --> 00:02:34,540
Just drink more water.

45
