♪My wish is simple♪

47
00:02:42,460 --> 00:02:43,660
Sis, I'm off to school.

48
00:02:46,460 --> 00:02:47,380
Morning.

49
00:02:47,820 --> 00:02:49,740
Hey, can you throw out

50
00:02:49,740 --> 00:02:50,700
the trash every night?

51
00:02:50,700 --> 00:02:51,860
So many flies.

52
00:02:52,340 --> 00:02:53,980
Isn't this your job?

53
00:02:55,510 --> 00:03:01,030
♪Free and true to myself♪

54
00:03:15,520 --> 00:03:16,460
Oh, my gosh.

55
00:03:16,460 --> 00:03:18,260
Chop it finer.

56
00:03:18,260 --> 00:03:20,100
Listen, this way works too.

57
00:03:20,100 --> 00:03:21,340
It's all scallions anyway.

58
00:03:22,180 --> 00:03:23,020
Stop.

59
00:03:23,180 --> 00:03:25,610
♪You make everything I want perfect♪

60
