♪Like a fearless and brave freedom♪

64
00:03:38,060 --> 00:03:38,900
Good.

65
00:03:38,900 --> 00:03:41,440
♪I'm the answer to everything you want♪

66
00:03:42,220 --> 00:03:43,060
Careful, careful.

67
00:03:43,420 --> 00:03:44,460
Time to cook the noodles.

68
