481
00:26:59,660 --> 00:27:00,660
So pungent.

482
00:27:01,660 --> 00:27:02,940
I planted some scallions.

483
00:27:05,850 --> 00:27:07,340
Jiang Fang even went

484
00:27:07,340 --> 00:27:08,080
