- Of course, I do.

486
00:27:09,800 --> 00:27:11,020
Every piece of info I found

487
00:27:11,020 --> 00:27:12,020
is real,

488
00:27:12,020 --> 00:27:13,550
and the daily itinerary is right here.

489
00:27:14,900 --> 00:27:16,300
She even went to Dahuanglou?

490
00:27:17,780 --> 00:27:18,780
