543
00:29:12,020 --> 00:29:13,300
The bitterness of love?

544
00:29:14,580 --> 00:29:15,740
The bitterness of love...

545
00:29:18,300 --> 00:29:19,860
I've had plenty of other bitterness.

546
00:29:20,380 --> 00:29:21,700
Is love's bitterness worse?

547
00:29:23,460 --> 00:29:25,380
You could say I'm cursed.

548
00:29:25,500 --> 00:29:27,180
