550
00:29:28,620 --> 00:29:30,060
Including my old friend.

551
00:29:30,860 --> 00:29:31,700
Who?

552
00:29:32,540 --> 00:29:33,460
Lu.

553
00:29:36,940 --> 00:29:38,780
