554
00:29:38,780 --> 00:29:40,180
If you help me,

555
00:29:40,180 --> 00:29:41,420
I'll return the favor.

556
00:29:43,180 --> 00:29:44,540
No favors are needed.

557
00:29:45,420 --> 00:29:46,580
Just tell me how I can help.

558
00:29:50,860 --> 00:29:51,900
Tang Shuangshuang.

559
00:29:53,020 --> 00:29:53,860
Let me see.

560
00:29:54,020 --> 00:29:54,900
This one won't do.

561
00:29:54,900 --> 00:29:55,820
Come out.

562
00:29:55,820 --> 00:29:57,020
This one really won't do.

563
00:29:57,020 --> 00:29:57,980
Hurry and come out.

564
00:29:57,980 --> 00:30:00,140
Your clothes are all too tight.

565
00:30:00,500 --> 00:30:01,500
They look great.

566
00:30:01,500 --> 00:30:02,660
Look in the mirror yourself.

567
00:30:03,340 --> 00:30:04,820
This part needs to go lower.

568
00:30:04,820 --> 00:30:05,700
It can't.

569
00:30:05,700 --> 00:30:06,980
You need to show your shoulders.

570
00:30:06,980 --> 00:30:08,460
Not everyone can pull this off.

571
00:30:08,940 --> 00:30:10,500
Wow, your figure is pretty good.

572
00:30:11,340 --> 00:30:12,180
Listen.

573
00:30:12,300 --> 00:30:14,460
There can be absolutely
no mistakes this weekend.

574
00:30:14,460 --> 00:30:15,900
Not one mistake is allowed.

575
00:30:15,900 --> 00:30:17,300
If you mess this up,

576
00:30:17,300 --> 00:30:19,740
it'll be my farewell party
to the local socialite circle.

577
00:30:19,740 --> 00:30:20,820
Anyway,

578
00:30:20,820 --> 00:30:22,580
remember my reminders that day.

579
00:30:22,580 --> 00:30:24,520
One of my hands will cover
