898
00:52:00,780 --> 00:52:02,060
But I can fight!

899
00:52:03,460 --> 00:52:05,220
I can only fight!

900
00:52:05,740 --> 00:52:06,580
Is that enough?

901
00:52:09,460 --> 00:52:10,300
I...

902
00:52:13,430 --> 00:52:14,300
Enough, enough.

903
00:52:14,300 --> 00:52:15,930
Stop it.

904
00:52:35,700 --> 00:52:37,980
Why doesn't my mom love me?

905
00:52:40,260 --> 00:52:42,500
Why doesn't she want me?

906
00:52:44,300 --> 00:52:46,460
I'm just a burden.

907
