912
00:53:25,340 --> 00:53:26,940
Why can't she love me?

913
00:53:28,950 --> 00:53:31,210
Why does no one love me?

914
00:53:42,200 --> 00:53:43,130
Idiot.

915
00:54:00,420 --> 00:54:01,340
Why?

916
00:54:02,600 --> 00:54:03,500
Why?

